    <h1>Privacy Policy for PiMetaConnect</h1>
    <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 27, 2025</p>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to PiMetaConnect! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our application.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following information when you use PiMetaConnect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Username:</strong> Your Pi Network username, which is collected when you log in using Pi SDK.</li>
      <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Details related to payments made through Pi Network, such as payment IDs and transaction IDs.</li>
      <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Information such as your IP address, browser type, and device information may be collected automatically.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Authenticate your identity when you log in.</li>
      <li>Process payments made through the app.</li>
      <li>Improve the functionality and user experience of PiMetaConnect.</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored securely in a MongoDB database hosted on MongoDB Atlas. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, loss, or theft.</p>

    <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties, except as required by law or to process payments through Pi Network.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access the personal information we hold about you.</li>
      <li>Request the deletion of your data.</li>
      <li>Contact us with any questions or concerns about your privacy.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <strong>support@pimetaconnect.com</strong> (you can replace this with your actual email).</p>
